come morning is a feature-length dramatic thriller written and directed by derrick sims . the film was produced by fabled motion pictures and shot in october 2011 in cleveland county , arkansas . come morning premiered october 21 , 2012 at the austin film festival . the film won a special jury award for cinematography at the 2013 oxford film festival and the best of fest award at the charles b. pierce film festival . in november 2013 , the film began a limited theatrical release , and it was released on blu-ray , dvd , and vod on september 23 , 2014 by monarch home entertainment and phase 4 films .